This app runs with Python3 and only has been tested and running on a Mac so far.

On Windows or Mac , open the command-prompt window or a terminal.

1. Type in the following to get OpenGL for Python:
> pip install PyOpenGL

2. Type in the following to get the wxPython:
> pip install -U wxPython

3. To run the app type:
> python ruibks-cube.py
